Class SolverKociemba

java.lang.Object
  de.uni_muenster.hugo.cubie.Solver
      de.uni_muenster.hugo.cubie.SolverKociemba
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable
public final class SolverKociemba
extends Solver

This class is not relevant for HuGO! and therefore no javadoc documentation was done. One exception is the method setPosition( CubePosition cubePos, boolean test ) which is used once in an instantiation to check for solvability of a cube state. The code is documented by a simple documentation inside the class. It is part of the applet Cubie by Jaap Scherphuis © 2003-2004. The graphical visualization of the cube contained in Cubie is used for the GUI of the genetic solver. This class is left in the project to keep the applet intact.

Author:
Jaap Scherphuis
